## Deploy Model (Do Not Change)

The deploy flow is:
```bash
# Local development
docker compose --profile local up

# Production (on VPS after SSH + git pull)
docker compose --profile prod run --rm api pnpm mikro-orm migration:up
docker compose --profile prod up -d --build
docker image prune -f
```

`compose.yml` profiles:
- `local` — all services, hot reload, no Caddy
- `prod` — all services, built images, Caddy with auto SSL

imgproxy sidecar in `compose.yml`:
```yaml
imgproxy:
  image: darthsim/imgproxy:latest
  profiles: [local, prod]
  environment:
    IMGPROXY_USE_S3: "true"
    IMGPROXY_S3_ENDPOINT: http://minio:9000
    AWS_ACCESS_KEY_ID: ${MINIO_ROOT_USER}
    AWS_SECRET_ACCESS_KEY: ${MINIO_ROOT_PASSWORD}
    IMGPROXY_KEY: ${IMGPROXY_KEY}
    IMGPROXY_SALT: ${IMGPROXY_SALT}
  depends_on:
    - minio
```

