## What To Build First (Ordered)

1. `VideoHero.tsx` — server component, full viewport, muted video, gradient overlay, headline + CTA
2. `GifProductSection.tsx` — server component, 3-panel grid, short video loops, service CTAs
3. `UGCGallery.tsx` — client component shell + RSC data fetch, 4-col grid, hover states
4. `instagram.service.ts` — Express service, token management, 6hr cron, Postgres upsert
5. `/api/instagram/feed` route — filtered, approved posts, paginated
6. `EmblaCarousel.tsx` — reusable carousel for testimonials and service cards
7. `BeforeAfterSlider.tsx` — react-compare-slider wrapper with gold handle styling
8. `ServicesGrid.tsx` — server component, pricing, service descriptions
9. `BookingFlow.tsx` — multi-step client component, availability, Stripe deposit

Do not build the admin dashboard, auth system, or booking flow until components 1–3 are pixel-perfect and the design system is locked.

