## Acceptance Criteria for Priority Components

### VideoHero
- [ ] Plays on first load in Chrome, Safari iOS, Firefox
- [ ] Poster image visible before video loads
- [ ] No layout shift on load (explicit height: 100svh)
- [ ] Does not autoplay when `prefers-reduced-motion` is set
- [ ] Gradient overlay makes text legible at all viewport widths
- [ ] CTA button navigates to `/book`

### GifProductSection
- [ ] 3 panels fetch from `/api/services/featured` at build time
- [ ] Videos loop seamlessly with no flash between loops
- [ ] Hover border + overlay transition is under 200ms
- [ ] Grid collapses to single column below 768px

### UGCGallery
- [ ] 12 posts render from cached Postgres data (not live Instagram API)
- [ ] VIDEO posts autoplay in grid, IMAGE posts render as WebP via imgproxy
- [ ] Clicking any post opens Instagram permalink in new tab
- [ ] Grid reflows to 2 columns on mobile
- [ ] "Follow us" CTA links to the studio's Instagram profile
